com.rbbn.cpaas.mobile.presence.api

Interface PresenceSource


  • public interface PresenceSource
    A PresenceSource is a presentity representing the user of the API. A client should create a PresenceSource in order to publish the user's status. A PresenceSource has an associated time-to-live specified by the server.
